{"tid":1113601,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"真正用遊戲做嘅香港","createTime":"2019-04-18T04:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T05:15:42.000Z","uid":249119,"like":52,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a621c3057d7781940103cf47a06529cdb31600","tid":1113601,"uid":249119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"今日見到有人分享咗景三嘅《香港重建計劃》<br />\n見到佢用city skyline整咗一個香港出嚟<br />\n稍為睇咗佢嘅YouTube 都整得唔錯<br />\n不過建築、道路、地圖比例就唔係畫得幾好啦<br />\n<br />\n大約幾個月前 我整咗個1:1香港<br />\n花咗好多時間一直喺度整 見到景三嘅《香港重建計劃》我就想同大家分享下我整出尼嘅香港<br />\n道路建築位置、街道同埋地圖大多數都係跟足比例去整 宜家諗返嗰陣時正真係一啲都唔容易 花咗好多好多時間<br />\n<br />\n以下係我整嗰個香港嘅相！<br />\n希望大家鍾意啦<br />\n尼啲先叫做真正嘅用遊戲整嘅香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sf5PQP5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsf5PQP5.jpg&h=703b4aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jn2OmWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJn2OmWM.jpg&h=0f357ead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYOaAgN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYOaAgN.jpg&h=4539d1ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmetmWO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmetmWO.jpg&h=7b96a9e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NekXu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NekXu9.jpg&h=08b024d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6OwvAgQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OwvAgQ.jpg&h=0ae47c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNxR392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNxR392.jpg&h=ddfed676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/om2CfgJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fom2CfgJ.jpg&h=2d36a42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BzZMS3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBzZMS3p.jpg&h=579d2b6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60272cdbf9c9027fde6f7419c03db3620dded968","tid":1113601,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"夜景個啲好真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c114577f72dea75fb85d66341ed2805019713b","tid":1113601,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:26:12.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783fbceb8873e9517fed84ab606cbd32789674b1","tid":1113601,"uid":203696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:26:48.000Z","msg":"勁！有冇片睇？"},{"pid":"ed71ceaa5047cc6cbf34997b0ccf96e4b38e618d","tid":1113601,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:28:28.000Z","msg":"痴線， 好多變態佬<br />\n要幾多時間整"},{"pid":"e957385146429fc2d8e2846a0550e8a68a012848","tid":1113601,"uid":249119,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"分享多幾張<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cok0Xxp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCok0Xxp.jpg&h=7da7dc62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8trSOD5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8trSOD5.jpg&h=bfb30f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDHCfi7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDHCfi7.jpg&h=670fe89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WCCfi8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WCCfi8.jpg&h=00159b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7650Xxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7650Xxv.jpg&h=135e5d30&s={SIZE}