By":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:42:47.000Z","msg":"有無地鐵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:44:10.000Z","msg":"暫時港島線 由堅尼地城整到去鰂魚涌站<br />\n荃灣線淨係整咗中環到尖沙咀"},{"pid":"f634c60552ba1c98d0ae0727dcc5c2b237d6d2f7","tid":1113601,"uid":180037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"可唔可以用係Flight Sim度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb50464781a52540408a14db47c48523b90e6d4f","tid":1113601,"uid":103879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴線佬"},{"pid":"7dce3a332c691c3a4ed97c777dceb05a676e9f4c","tid":1113601,"uid":249119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f634c60552ba1c98d0ae0727dcc5c2b237d6d2f7","tid":1113601,"uid":180037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"可唔可以用係Flight Sim度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:48:28.000Z","msg":"整完先算啦 而家淨係得維多利亞港兩岸<br />\n同埋呢個地圖唔會有整咗去機場"},{"pid":"dc4ba46df32483214d1b4ecb0aff29ce6d6c0531","tid":1113601,"uid":180037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7dce3a332c691c3a4ed97c777dceb05a676e9f4c","tid":1113601,"uid":249119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f634c60552ba1c98d0ae0727dcc5c2b237d6d2f7","tid":1113601,"uid":180037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"可唔可以用係Flight Sim度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/